data.description: Large 4 bedroom colonial situated on a quiet street and just 3 1/2 years young. Open concept first floor with the living room and eat in kitchen, great for gatherings. Hallway off kitchen leads to a half bathroom, access to the garage and an office space at the end. Sliding doors off kitchen open to a fully fenced in yard with a stamped concrete patio. Second floor includes master suite and 3 additional bedrooms, a second full bath and laundry room. Full basement has potential for more living space. Playground and basketball court are right across the street. Close highway access.
